{"type":"message","id":"bb679150","parentId":"144809a9","timestamp":"2026-04-07T14:16:17.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我有了完整的插件列表。让我整理一下与记忆/存储相关的插件。从列表中可以看到：\n\n**与记忆/存储相关的插件（已加载 + 已禁用）：**\n1. memory-core - 核心记忆搜索插件（disabled）\n2. memory-lancedb - LanceDB 向量数据库长期记忆插件（disabled）\n\n**可能的替代方案：**\n- 向量嵌入模型：huggingface（已加载）- 可以用于 embedding\n- 其他存储：没有看到其他类似的记忆插件\n\n让我再查一下有没有其他与知识库、向量相关的插件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_05b05292d33a48d488d58835","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/ | grep -iE \"(memory|vector|embed|store|db|knowledge| KB|wiki)\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":28164,"output":193,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28357,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775571373539,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3de0d3be-3445-44cc-969b-30d753d0906d"}}
