{"type":"message","id":"b3320714","parentId":"51d6f290","timestamp":"2026-04-07T14:17:29.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想启用 memory-core 和 memory-lancedb 插件。我需要修改 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 来启用这两个插件。\n\n首先读取当前的配置，然后修改 plugins.entries 中 memory-core 和 memory-lancedb 的 enabled 字段为 true。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，我来启用这两个插件：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4a3b73d85bc749f3955b5f01","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":28457,"output":89,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28546,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775571447662,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9fd7a77c-1572-4e8f-81d8-1770ccbafb06"}}
